{"tid":1367094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［臨急抱佛腳系列］727元朗，200蚊內買齊野餐基本裝備","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:59.000Z","uid":100291,"like":178,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7d2d859e66bc5e4b48614ab94145d065f70cee","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"由於727太多人表示想去元朗參加宗教活動/睇戲/食飯<br />\n但721元朗發生既事件，人大家人心惶惶<br />\n所以為大家安心唔受傷地進行各種活動，以下有個基本既買裝備地點推薦<br />\n<br />\n大家跟住去就可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>200蚊內買齊基本既保護裝備</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n首先，第一站可以去<strong>深水場電子特賣城</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可購裝備：面罩5蚊，背囊9蚊，冰巾3蚊</span><br />\n關門時間：22:30<br />\n大家可以去到深水埗站<br />\n由D2出口出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8roDBWd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8roDBWd.png&h=8e8ee3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向住麥當勞方向走一分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwgRcve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwgRcve.png&h=9055fce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUJDBW6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUJDBW6.png&h=b9de2b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bayW73Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbayW73Y.png&h=a9690ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Z8DBXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Z8DBXk.png&h=b486f4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mnbtZaG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmnbtZaG.png&h=abf50e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9Qq1o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9Qq1o3.png&h=51d8ee94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eg9WoCq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEg9WoCq.png&h=e1b5cc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二站，<strong>迪卡儂</strong><br />\n關門時間：22:30<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可購裝備：浮潛鏡 ，太撚多 睇圖</span><br />\n就可以搭我地準時率99%既港鐵去旺角站<br />\n旺角既E1出口 一出就見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMrqgX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMrqgX7.png&h=9303cd8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0oL1p9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0oL1p9.png&h=7a790fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nahg75a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnahg75a.png&h=19794000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNK7vix.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNK7vix.png&h=e1ce0e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2ayqRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2ayqRT.png&h=e5a3339d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n備註：迪卡隆嘅浮潛鏡可能同某d高級口罩/裝備唔夾，試清楚先<br />\n買完就出番去 去第三站啦<br />\n<br />\n第三站，<strong>先鋒極限裝備</strong><br />\n關門時間：19:30（通常）（19:30後都可以去碰下運氣）<br />\n廣東道918<br />\n一出迪卡儂向山東街行，轉個灣就到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可購裝備：頭盔 30蚊<br />\n（由於老闆自己公司既頭盔已經清曬，新果批係買行家拎番黎所以貴左十蚊，唔好誤會老闆食人血饅頭）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3V6LS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3V6LS2.png&h=296fbe55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tLJ8eMp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLJ8eMp.png&h=0069e7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsPrLS6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsPrLS6.png&h=d0c3f83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">最後埋數：面罩5蚊+背囊9蚊+冰巾3蚊+頭盔30蚊+迪卡儂既眼罩49蚊+足球護腳pad 69蚊=165蚊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其他淨低既仲可以買手套同其他裝備Tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後希望大家既活動活心又放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e0b336c0c6988ceb875bcbd7a18c983d06d56d8","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7dfdc80ce58a63ab2ba5d291296df6f050313ba","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafa692aff022598bb970adfb5f96655ee8bba53","tid":1367094,"uid":18082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970a20b4a1b3de1c9a16c1ac0640aab3c1fd1d23","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4896d2a79e7df0908db9ac2f4d42a4f423344cc","tid":1367094,"uid":208452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家入去填低感受</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdmxGktTO9MbC1TsNdGqfOPpgjLUgV9VzpD98fy3tLWCRmyig/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdmxGktTO9MbC1TsNdGqfOPpgjLUgV9VzpD98fy3tLWCRmyig%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=12cf6e88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdmxGktTO9MbC1TsNdGqfOPpgjLUgV9VzpD98fy3tLWCRmyig/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">希望大家Forward 個post 同 Google form link 出去，俾唔同年紀唔同行業都發到聲<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"398482c9d0de8d221c885a3906226195d9b79422","tid":1367094,"uid":73826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"478d684e9bfa52e02817cdc62588f752343f9939","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a03001347a64f3bcf18a450e2e918b0b9daa8fb","tid":1367094,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770945296c1cf29e4293d5839aab7e4666f0777d","tid":1367094,"uid":270613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"必推 辛苦哂師兄"},{"pid":"f4e889a6cac261d5382df82970a220c0d7a1e1bf","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:08:29.000Z","msg":"幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e8036ea33a19bd8b95f051d92a62f7ecbcd151","tid":1367094,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"推 保護好自己"},{"pid":"a2ea15fead12110eebf00bfac8cfb6dc1928324b","tid":1367094,"uid":100291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97958ecf0e1eeec8333d382cf0f8c126a6ba5e7a","tid":1367094,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"Good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi